    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "professionals don't really get it though. they want to \"fix\" the creativity, but it's not like a broken bone. it's more like the light has just gone out. how do you fix being empty? there's no spark left to reignite. it just feels like i'm occupying space that doesn't belong to me anymore.",
